    @CreoleResource(name="GATE .pubMed.txt document format",
                comment="Load this to allow the opening of PubMed text documents, and choose the mime type \"text/x-pubmed\"or use the correct file extension.",
                autoinstances=,
                isPrivate=true)
public class PubmedTextDocumentFormat
extends TextualDocumentFormat
    A document format analyser for PubMed text documents. Use mime type value "text/x-pubmed", or file extension ".pubmed.txt" to access this document format.
